name: Management Dashboard
description:
Managing your team is a boring task and to make it engaging, here are the dashboard screens. The dashboard screen is pixel perfected to make sure you don't hassle while managing your team and doing your great work.


The file supported is for eevry design software to make it easy for you to use it in your favorite software. The files are available for Figma. Adobe XD, Sketch, Photoshop, InVision Studio, and HTML (Starter). Cheers!
